title: [Tsutomu Mutsuki] Momoiro Peanuts v01 c01-03 [English Translated
description:
This is a sponsored project of mine that's been kinda slow in the works.  I recently completed Chapter 3. Chapters 1 and 2 have revised type-settings as well as some minor corrections.  They are included in this file.

This manga includes has both BB and somewhat loli themes.  The character on the cover I believe may be 18, but petite, from what I can gather thus far.
